addEntity(address,string,string,string,s.details: function that allows you to add a entity to the entities mapping

params._active: a flag that shows if a entity is active or not
params._addressEntity: the address that identify the entity in the blockchain
params._url_AOA: the url that contains the AOA of the entity
params._url_createAID: the url that contains the alastria ID of the entity
params._url_logo: the url that contains the logo of the entity

entitiesList().details: function that return the list of entities that are registered in the blockchain
